description: The Manx government believes some 169 residents are currently stuck outside the Isle of Man.
title: Coronavirus: IOM residents to be repatriated in 'staggered' way
title_page: Coronavirus: IOM residents to be repatriated in 'staggered' way - BBC News
maintext: Even if they reached the UK, they would not be able to enter the Isle of Man until restrictions are lifted or they are invited to do so.
